MatrosDMS – Technology Study License
===================================

Copyright (c) YEAR MatrosDMS

This project is primarily developed as a technology study and reference
implementation. Its goal is to explore and demonstrate modern approaches
to document management systems, including architecture, data processing,
search, and automation.

The software is made available under a dual-licensing model

